description: Commands to manage network service design version resources.

commands.name: az aosm publisher network-service-design version list
commands.summary: List information about the network service design versions available under the specified network service design group.
commands.syntax:
az aosm publisher network-service-design version list --group-name
                                                      --publisher-name
                                                      --resource-group
                                                      [--max-items]
                                                      [--next-token]
examples: az aosm publisher network-function-definition version list --resource-group contoso-aosm --publisher-name contoso --group-name contoso-service

commands.name: az aosm publisher network-service-design version show
commands.summary: Get information about a network service design version.
commands.syntax:
az aosm publisher network-service-design version show [--group-name]
                                                      [--ids]
                                                      [--publisher-name]
                                                      [--resource-group]
                                                      [--subscription]
                                                      [--version-name]

commands.name: az aosm publisher network-service-design version update-state
commands.summary: Update network service design version state.
commands.syntax:
az aosm publisher network-service-design version update-state [--group-name]
                                                              [--ids]
                                                              [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                                              [--publisher-name]
                                                              [--resource-group]
                                                              [--subscription]
                                                              [--version-name]
                                                              [--version-state {Active, Deprecated, Preview, Unknown}]
examples: az aosm publisher network-service-design version update-state --resource-group contoso-aosm --publisher-name contoso --group-name contoso-service --version-name 1.0.0 --version-state Deprecated
